race.comment: BEE EXACT (7) missed here two back when favourite before another good performance at Ipswich most recently. The 3kg claim comes in handy and he has the speed to roll across from the draw. Track and trip winner previously and can put his best foot forward. THE IMMORTALS (6) won two back over this course and distance to break his maiden before a disappointing effort at Ipswich last time out. Drawn well again today and he returns to the scene of the crime. Can bounce back to his best. GIGGY (1) missed narrowly at Ipswich last start and that form looks to stack up here. Can go close again. COOL PANELS (5) has claims here first-up.
